ComicInfo.Summary:
Jim is paid a visit by the biggest guest-star of all - God. Jim's ambitious attempts to discover his identity literally lead him to the pearly gates.
Meanwhile, his celebrity status begins to take a toll on his relationships with those trying to help him, but he's one step closer to finding the answers he's looking for.
